      • InspectorGridBagLayout

        public InspectorGridBagLayout(javax.swing.JPanel panel,
                              float idAnchorFactor)
        Creates a new InspectorGridBagLayout object.
        Parameters:
        panel - the panel to use.
        idAnchorFactor - this is used to anchor IDs either at the top or center of a row. If you divide the height of the right hand side by the height of the left hand side and is less than this factor: the id is centered. Otherwise the id is anchored at the top.
